1. *Malena* je danas otišla u školu. (Little Malena went to school today.)
2. Sinoć sam gledao film *malene* Japanske glumice. (Last night I watched a movie starring a petite Japanese actress.)
3. Imam *malenu* ideju kako da to uradimo. (I have a small idea on how we can do that.)
4. *Malenoj* maci je potreban veterinar. (The little cat needs a vet.)
5. Kupila sam *malenu* kutiju čokolade za njegov rođendan. (I bought a small box of chocolate for his birthday.)
6. *Malena* prodavnica u mom kraju ima najbolje krofne. (The small shop in my neighborhood has the best donuts.)
7. *Malena* beba spava u krevetiću. (The little baby is sleeping in the crib.)
8. *Maleni* cvet je divan dodatak tvojoj kosi. (The small flower is a lovely addition to your hair.)
9. *Malene* ruke joj treba da ti pomognu oko tog posla. (Her little hands can help you with that task.)
10. *Malena* kućica na drvetu je omiljeno mesto za igru. (The small treehouse is a favorite play spot.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "malena" can be translated to "little" or "small" in English, depending on the context.